channel.title: Appraisal for this RS related website
channel.description:
I bought "Runeshop.com" for $250 US, havent bought any hosting for it yet, and was going to make it into a RS market (and account market). It was created in 2002, and thinking of selling it now. How much is this site worth?
*I know advertising isnt allowed but their has never been any content on this site.
